{"tid":783603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖開咧]#馮盈盈 陳嘉倩 李靜儀 倪晨曦 鄧麗欣 陳法拉 18-19 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽第一輪投選專區","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T04:26:31.000Z","uid":92376,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea5303f5ff02e30cd9d3d178fe8b644491d1aa9","tid":783603,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n張曦雯 : 李佳芯<br />\n杜小喬 : 鄧麗欣<br />\n李靜儀@SG : 馮盈盈<br />\n苟芸慧 : 陳瀅<br />\n陳嘉倩 : 謝安琪<br />\n陳穎欣@SG : 文詠珊<br />\n沈卓盈 : 倪晨曦<br />\n朱千雪 : 麥明詩<br />\n林嘉欣 : 陳法拉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=ZNJE44%2FX61GjFTrrixCz7DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=27785a29\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8786196dd8bfab85519c92e6a1d1933ac0b6619","tid":783603,"uid":27970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1412d60aa4a8f0bed39b2dbcc941ddfbcf439f","tid":783603,"uid":92376,"like":94,"dislike":441,"score":-347,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽第一輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-8-18 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NK2BTLt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNK2BTLt.png&h=e8aa85b3&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Edm3OXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEdm3OXT.png&h=95cb63e4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">張曦雯vs李佳芯</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div>"},{"pid":"e63827c34e60a73ccddaaffd271b848bc768b2f2","tid":783603,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"0b6a37b3b57cf7de72ef5a504a246d778fceb7e3","tid":783603,"uid":92376,"like":92,"dislike":434,"score":-342,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-8-18 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OlQADnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOlQADnD.png&h=73e28921&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8soY8NT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8soY8NT.png&h=9425f541&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">杜小喬vs鄧麗欣</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</d